<h2>Brief Description</h2>
<p data-start="0" data-end="394" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node=""><span data-start="0" data-end="24" data-is-only-node="">Parks and Recreation</span> departments are responsible for managing public parks, recreational facilities, and community programs. They maintain green spaces, playgrounds, sports fields, trails, and public gardens. They also organize recreational activities, youth and adult sports leagues, fitness classes, cultural events, and summer camps to promote health, wellness, and community engagement.</p>
